name: Wonder WC Checkout Review
author: Wonderjar Creative

sections.description: Eliminate ordering mistakes from your WooCommerce store. Present your customers with a clean and comprehensive checkout review and summary. The process happens after the customer clicking the submit button and after the checkout data is validated, but before the order processes. Options and text are configurable.
